messages.message: Just put a PR to avoid throwing an error when start_x is null or non-existant: instabase/pull/70193 (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/70193). The root cause of `start_x` and `start_y` being null when there's a mismatch between word and raw_word is still not fixed though. Should we create another ticket for @Nikolaos Kofinas to investigate? cc @Serena @Kaustubh (KD)
